{
  "stem": "26142.9",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You look at this mountain, there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, in Ukrainian, he said, you see this [UKRAINIAN] over there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he used the word [UKRAINIAN] which was a little bit strange to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't catch on the word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [UKRAINIAN] in Ukrainian, means an open space inside a forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They call that [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, do you see that on top of that mountain?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The [UKRAINIAN]?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, when it's going to get dark, around 4 o'clock, 5 o'clock-- in the end of October, it's getting dark already that time-- he said, you try to get up to this [UKRAINIAN] and at the edge of that place, you'll stay there.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I'll come, and it'll be about 4:30 or 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll be there, and from there I'm going to take you and show you which way to cross the border.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It got dark, and we got out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember now, we started running till we get to this [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But fortunately, we tried to get lost among the trees, because the trees came down only to a certain place and the other place was empty.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were running toward-- which was not very wise to do because this, in itself, made us suspicious, but that's the way we did it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went into this here-- once we got lost in the forest, we came to the [UKRAINIAN] and when we got there, we all of a sudden hear voices.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What voices?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it turned out we had a little scare that that was shepherds that were gathering-- they had sheep on that [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were gathering them up, and they were talking to themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they didn't see us, and they got away.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
